00:21:33,501 --> 00:21:37,087
The hero Napoleon Bonaparte said,

324
00:21:38,130 --> 00:21:43,719
"A true hero is the one who overcomes the misfortunes of life."

325
00:21:44,345 --> 00:21:46,138
Above and beyond,

326
00:21:47,848 --> 00:21:50,601
Plus Ultra!

327
00:21:53,103 --> 00:21:56,649
And everyone, have a good time!

328
00:22:04,281 --> 00:22:06,617
